    rdfs:comment 'Summary of regulatory compliance obligations specified in the contract, such as HIPAA Business Associate Agreement (BAA) terms, GDPR data processing terms, FDA Quality System Regulation (QSR) requirements, or GxP compliance for clinical products. Critical for IVD and clinical genomics contracts.' ;
